### 1. 查询历史记录（测试服务是否正常）
GET http://localhost:8080/api/resource/history

### 2. 生成教学大纲
POST http://localhost:8080/api/resource/syllabus
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": "Java编程基础"
}

### 3. 生成PPT大纲
POST http://localhost:8080/api/resource/ppt
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": "数据结构"
}

### 4. 生成练习题
POST http://localhost:8080/api/resource/exercise
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": "MySQL数据库"
}

### 5. 生成思维导图
POST http://localhost:8080/api/resource/mindmap
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": "计算机网络"
}

### 6. 生成复习提纲
POST http://localhost:8080/api/resource/review
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": "操作系统"
}

### 7. 下载PPT文件（会下载.pptx文件）
POST http://localhost:8080/api/resource/ppt/download
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "input": "人工智能"
}